  <h2>Accessible Tourism</h2>
  <p>The Ith-Region is continuously working to make tourism accessible to all.</p>
  <h3>Accessible Paths</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Barrier-free circular walks</strong> – Suitable for wheelchairs and pushchairs</li>
    <li><strong>Easy walking paths</strong> – Level paths through the villages</li>
    <li><strong>Rest areas</strong> – Regular seating along the routes</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Further Accessible Offerings</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Ith-Sole Spa</strong> – Barrier-free access to pools and sauna</li>
    <li><strong>Selected accommodation</strong> – Wheelchair-accessible holiday apartments</li>
  </ul>
